    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT219-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">ciṟaippuṟam. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Hedge. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT219">
        <lg type="edition">

          <l>pacappeṉ mēṉi yatuvē nayappavar</l>
          <l>nāri ṉeñcat tāriṭai yatuvē</l>
          <l>ceṟivuñ cēṇikan taṉṟē yaṟivē</l>
          <l>yāṅkaṭ celka meḻukeṉa vīṅkē</l>
          <l>vallā kūṟi yirukku muḷḷilait</l>
          <l>taṭavunilait tāḻaic cērppaṟ</l>
          <l>kiṭamaṟ ṟōḻiyeṉ ṉīrō veṉiṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l>Pale is my body. Longing [is] in a place</l>
          <l>difficult [to reach], in his heart devoid of attachment.</l>
          <l>Even restraint stayed aside in the distance. Knowledge.</l>
          <l>To say here: “we shall go there, rise!”</l>
          <l>If I were to say : “of what kind [are] you?”, friend,</l>
          <l rend="indent5">[that] indeed [would be] the opportunity for</l>
          <l rend="indent2">for the man from the coast of thorny-leafed, broad-based Tāḻai trees,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">who permanently talks without being able [to act].</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="3-5b" resp="#TVG">
            <l>Knowledge is speaking to me , unable [to act]: “we'll go there, rise!”</l>
          </lg>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
